{"id": 2694, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都受不了哪些特别自我的社交习惯？", "description": "日本网友总结了两种社交障碍，一种是社恐，一种就是“不招人待见还不自知”的阳性社交障碍。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 4656, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181226105617ltzjpH5MSYUDCvcx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-07T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 318720, "content": "讲起自己的事就停不下来", "image": null, "praise_count": 391, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321280, "content": "不把自己当外人", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716803}, {"id": 333057, "content": "永远在索取 盲目自大 听不进意见 感觉自己什么都是对的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 318721, "content": "永远有办法把话题转到自己身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 349, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 318722, "content": "宽以律己，严以待人", "image": null, "praise_count": 438, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321282, "content": "言谈之中总是一副我很了不起看不起别人还觉得自己很公正的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551501}, {"id": 318723, "content": "察觉不到别人的情绪变化，开起玩笑来没个度", "image": null, "praise_count": 792, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321283, "content": "看到楼上提到“情商”深有同感，周围好些人怕是压根就不懂那词还TM时常挂在嘴上。拜托，油腔滑调、圆滑世故那不叫情商。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441303}, {"id": 318724, "content": "遇事总是自然地责怪伙伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 281, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321284, "content": "弹幕的一种格式 前面说xx的是xxx吗 你不知道xxx会xxx吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358179}, {"id": 321285, "content": "永远把自己摆在首位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551517}, {"id": 321288, "content": "总打断人说话，然后自己喋喋不休\n对我就是这样，面试落选了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460062}, {"id": 321289, "content": "不关心别人的感受，想怎样就怎样，以为这是自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709849}, {"id": 321290, "content": "只相信自己以为的“事实”", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551023}, {"id": 321291, "content": "讨厌自来熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504532}, {"id": 321292, "content": "自我感觉别人跟他关系好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819794}, {"id": 322574, "content": "总是和别人抬杠，当你指出来他在抬杠的时候，他就说你在抬杠，然后你再反驳他在抬杠，然后彼此就一直抬一直抬。。。直到你停止。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557445}, {"id": 321295, "content": "“我告诉你吧balabala……”，“行了行了行了哎呀…”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551570}, {"id": 322575, "content": "触摸个人边界 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557445}, {"id": 322322, "content": "学不会倾听", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555775}, {"id": 321556, "content": "喜欢无端给别人提意见：“我觉得你就是…你应该…”“你怎么不…啊”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342695}, {"id": 321557, "content": "总觉得自己都对 喜欢说话给人添堵 🙄️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532026}, {"id": 321559, "content": "看似安慰别人，实则在嘲笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414596}, {"id": 321307, "content": "言谈举止都要旁敲侧击体现自己多么厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424722}, {"id": 321308, "content": "下意识否认别人的观点无论对错。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551619}, {"id": 321309, "content": "自己存在问题也说自己知道，但是要求别人体谅而且不改", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551622}, {"id": 321316, "content": "满嘴跑火车，天天吹牛逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551633}, {"id": 321317, "content": "八句话不离自己的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551636}, {"id": 322599, "content": "过于敏感，经常莫名冷战又不说原因，自己孤立别人，还觉得别人孤立她委屈。让别人猜，太累了，活着就很累了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454097}, {"id": 321323, "content": "和朋友聊天总喜欢攀比", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551641}, {"id": 321582, "content": "慢慢负能量，时时刻刻都再抱怨，", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552540}, {"id": 321330, "content": "说认真你就输了……我可去你的吧   不认真我就能赢么？这样那就不要和我讨论ok!!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551645}, {"id": 321331, "content": "以自我为中心的输出", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500545}, {"id": 322101, "content": "总觉得自己对别人恩重如山，时刻要让别人感恩戴德。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554600}, {"id": 322626, "content": "没有硬实力 偏偏爱装逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557864}, {"id": 321347, "content": "虚伪的关心  拉叫式点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496756}, {"id": 321350, "content": "事不关己高高挂起，事若关己，听不得一点客观的，不利于自己的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487959}, {"id": 323144, "content": "一直在说自己的事情；出现分歧一定要和别人讨论争到自己对为止；关系不够熟的时候过问打探别人的隐私。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559623}, {"id": 321353, "content": "对于，不熟的人不知道如何回答她的间题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551668}, {"id": 321609, "content": "惹了祸之后第一反应是赖这个赖那个，从不去找自身的问题，吗的", "image": "img/option/option/20190108195649v2besHhCSn1XkFpf", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552612}, {"id": 321354, "content": "以自我为中心的谈话", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 321611, "content": "收到消息不回\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552634}, {"id": 321357, "content": "不知道如何和不熟的人说话，和不熟的人在一起会非常尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551668}, {"id": 321358, "content": "开得起别人玩笑，别人开不得自己玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477371}, {"id": 321614, "content": "感觉不到别人的情绪变化。将自己的恶意强加给别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533277}, {"id": 321615, "content": "感觉不到别人的情绪变化，把自己的理解强加到别人身上，开起玩笑来没度。 无故打扰人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533277}, {"id": 321362, "content": "总不记得自己说过什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551680}, {"id": 321619, "content": "只能听得懂别人表达出来的表面意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542766}, {"id": 321620, "content": "自我感觉和别人关系良好，无故打扰人。自以为是麻烦别人。最讨厌一厢情愿，自来熟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533277}, {"id": 321365, "content": "吃饭吧唧嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528961}]}